title: NORTH KOREA | SCIENTOLOGY | TAKING ON PUTIN WITH JOHN SWEENEY
description:
Well renowned British investigative journalist, John Sweeney best know for his work at BBC Panorama gives an authentic and powerful insight in life undercover.
